pageProduct.name: SUP Inner Glow Collagen 30 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Collagen boosting for glowy, firm skin.

BEAUTY BEGINS WITHIN
Collagen is one of the key building blocks of our skin that helps keep it silky soft and plumpl However, as the years go by, our body's natural production of collagen depletes. SUP helps boost collagen production and skin elasticity and firmness, minus the one-hour skin routine.

WHY POP SUP?
Our team of naturopaths have combined key ingredients like Vitamin C, Biotin and Resveratrol in a daily matrix of 3000mg of Collagen peptides to help:
- Support skin elasticity and firmness
- Maintain healthy hair, skin and nails
- Fight free radical damage to help reduce signs of ageing like fine lines and wrinkles
- Boost collagen production
POPSUP

Size: 30 Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• Support skin elasticity and firmness
• Maintain healthy hair, skin and nails
• Fight free radical damage to help reduce signs of ageing like fine lines and wrinkles
• Boost collagen production
• 3000mg of Collagen per serve

Warnings

Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing. Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Contains gluten, soya beans, phenylalanine and sulfites. Reseal immediately after use.

Ingredients

Silicon (as silicon dioxide) 15mg
Reynoutria japonica root ext. dry conc. standardised 20mg
Equiv. to Reynoutria japonica root dry 1.9g (min)
Equiv. to Resveratrol (of Reynoutria japonica) 10mg
Zinc (as zinc amino acid chelate) 3mg
Ascorbic acid (Vitamin C) 12mg
Biotin 2mg
Hydrolysed collagen 1000mg

Contains: CONTAINS GLUTEN, SOYA BEANS, PHENYLALANINE & SULFITES.

Allergen Contains: Gluten| Phenylalanine| Soybean| Sulphites

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Peanuts

Directions

Adults
Take 1 tablet daily with food for general skin health support.
Take 1 tablet 3 times daily with food to help support skin elasticity and firmness or as advised by your healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C.
